This project is inspired by PinchChat (https://github.com/MarlBurroW/pinchchat)
created by MarlBurroW for OpenClaw.

The UI/UX design, layout concepts, and visual styling are heavily inspired by
PinchChat, while the implementation is original and built specifically for
the Hermes AI Agent ecosystem.

PinchChat is an excellent open-source chat interface for OpenClaw, and this
project aims to bring similar design principles to the Hermes community.

Original PinchChat Repository:
https://github.com/MarlBurroW/pinchchat

Attribution is retained in the README.md and this NOTICE file.

